ation ready (.po and .mo files availables) and you can easily customize it. Indeed, it has Widget ready sidebars, Valid <strong>XHTML</strong> / <strong>CSS</strong> and a Blog structure which supports threaded comments.</p>\n<h2>STYLE</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214215" alt="petshop2" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop2.png" width="964" height="272" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can compose your<strong> front page</strong> choosing your <strong>favourite</strong> <strong>slider</strong> to display your product and service. You have <strong>3</strong> <strong>options</strong>: <strong>flexislider</strong>, <strong>elegant</strong> <strong>slider</strong> and <strong>thumbnail</strong> <strong>slider</strong>.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">To customize your website using PetShopper you can set <strong>custom</strong> <strong>widgets</strong> and you can choose your favorite <strong>portfolio</strong> <strong>layout</strong> to show and share your projects. Furthermore, you can use <strong>unlimited</strong> <strong>contact</strong> <strong>form</strong> for your site and set up each form very easily through our panel.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can choose your <strong>Fonts</strong> &amp; <strong>Colors</strong> to completely customize your website:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Over<strong> 600 Google fonts</strong> ‚Äì google fonts list will be automatically updated;</li>\n<li>Set font and size for titles, slogan, body text and more;</li>\n<li>In the <strong>premium</strong> <strong>version</strong> of the theme you can easily edit the colors of all the sections and elements like text, links,slogan and so on.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>PRODUCTS PAGE</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-214217" alt="petshop3" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/petshop3.png" width="606" height="641" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">In the product‚Äôs page you can set the <strong>Wishlist</strong>, which gives to users the ab